          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="text-sky-600 font-black text-2xl flex-shrink-0">4</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900 text-xl">Mobile service request: 83% of searches on phones</p>
