          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="text-sky-600 font-black text-2xl flex-shrink-0">6</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-black text-gray-900 text-xl">Response time承诺: 78% more quote requests</p>
              <p class="text-gray-700 mt-2 leading-relaxed">Added "We Respond Within 2 Hours - Guaranteed" badge with average response time (47 minutes). Month 1: 78% more quote requests. Emergency = painful = homeowner waits for nobody. Fast response承诺 = you'll help soon = request quote.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MY EXPERIENCE: MIKE TORRES CASE STUDY -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-5xl">
