        <p class="text-sm font-black text-sky-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">THE BEFORE: 18 CALLS/MONTH, $12,600 REVENUE</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">Torres's website: 2016 template, stock photos of random AC units, no emergency service mentioned, services vague ("HVAC Solutions"), maintenance plan buried, no visible credentials. Phone number small, not clickable. "Request Quote" form broken 40% of time. Mobile: text tiny, buttons unclickable. Torres: "We do excellent work. 7 years in Phoenix, 500+ happy customers. But nobody found us online. AC breaks July, homeowner searches, sees our site from 2016, thinks 'out of business,' calls competitor with modern site. I was losing thousands in urgent repairs."</p>

        <p class="text-sm font-black text-sky-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">THE FIX: ONE WEEKEND, $1,500</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">Friday: chose Squarespace (professional business templates, mobile-responsive). Sunday night: launched new site with 1) "24/7 Emergency AC Repair - Arrive in 2 Hours" hero badge with click-to-call, 2) clear service pages (AC Repair, Installation, Maintenance, Furnace, Duct Cleaning), 3) maintenance plan page with pricing ($149/year), 4) "Licensed & Insured - License #AZ789XYZ" prominent, 5) mobile-optimized click-to-call button always visible, 6) "We Respond Within 2 Hours" guarantee, 7) real project photos (before/after), 8) customer testimonials with names/addresses.</p>

        <p class="text-sm font-black text-sky-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">THE AFTER: 112 CALLS/MONTH, $38,400 REVENUE, 205% INCREASE</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">Month 1: 67 calls (up from 18, 272% increase), $21,200 revenue. Emergency badge visible: urgent calls flooded in (47% of total). Services clear: homeowners knew Torres handled their problem = call him. Maintenance plan visible: 23 signups ($3,427 recurring). Mobile click-to-call: 83% calls from phones. Torres: "July heatwave, AC breaks at 3 AM, homeowner searches, sees our 24/7 badge, clicks call. We're there in 90 minutes. $4,200 job. Before: invisible. After: emergencies find us. Best $1,500 I ever spent."</p>

        <div class="border-l-[3px] border-sky-500 pl-6 py-5 bg-white/70 rounded-r mb-6">
          <p class="text-sm font-black text-sky-700 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">THE 90-DAY BREAKDOWN</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed"><strong>Month 1:</strong> 67 calls, $21,200 revenue, 272% increase. Emergency badge + services clear + mobile click-to-call = immediate results.<br><strong>Month 2:</strong> 89 calls, $29,800 revenue. Added maintenance plan FAQ + testimonials with photos.<br><strong>Month 3:</strong> 112 calls, $38,400 revenue. 42 maintenance plan customers ($6,258/month recurring). 205% total increase in 90 days. Investment: $1,500. ROI: 2,460%.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE HARD TRUTH -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-sky-50">
