      <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-sky-300 p-8 md:p-10 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">Why Squarespace Wins for Building Trust</p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">1. Professional Business Templates</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Squarespace's business templates communicate reliability and professionalism. Clean layouts, strong typography, organized sections. Perfect for HVAC contractors wanting to establish legitimacy. Homeowners see professional site = trust contractor = call for service.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">2. Service Showcase Pages</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Create dedicated pages for each service: AC Repair, Installation, Maintenance, Furnace Service. Add descriptions, photos, pricing info. Homeowner sees you handle their specific problem = qualified quote request. Organized services = clarity = calls.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">3. Contact Forms with Auto-Response</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Built-in forms integrate with email. Auto-reply confirms "We received your request, will respond within 2 hours." Homeowner gets peace of mind. One contractor saw 67% more quote requests after adding auto-response承诺.</p>
