            <p class="text-gray-700">Build authority with helpful content: "5 Signs Your AC Needs Repair," "How to Lower Your Energy Bill." Google rewards fresh content with higher rankings. Blog = traffic = leads = customers.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-[3px] border-sky-500 pl-6 py-5 bg-sky-50 rounded-r mt-8">
          <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Best For:</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">HVAC contractors prioritizing professional appearance, trust-building, service showcase. Not ideal if you need complex booking workflows beyond basic scheduling.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- DETAILED BREAKDOWN: WIX -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-5xl">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8">Wix AI for HVAC Companies</h2>

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-sky-50 border-[3px] border-sky-200 p-8 md:p-10 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">Why Wix Wins for Service Bookings</p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">1. Wix Bookings Built-In</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Native booking system handles everything: service types, duration, pricing, staff assignments, calendar sync. Customers book 24/7 without calling. One contractor reduced phone calls by 53% while increasing bookings by 67%.</p>
