            <p class="text-gray-700">20+ service business templates designed for contractors. Pre-built sections for services, testimonials, emergency contact, team profiles. Faster setup than Squarespace. Choose template, add your info, launch.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">3. Mobile App Management</p>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Manage bookings, update calendar, respond to inquiries from Wix mobile app. Get push notifications for new bookings. Perfect for contractors on-the-go between jobs.</p>
