      <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-sky-300 p-8 md:p-10 rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-2xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-6">Why Webflow Wins for Custom Service Pages</p>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
